      "rationale": "Testing was performed at a single load application rate (25 mm/min) and a single offset distance (50 mm per ASTM F1717). While this is the standard F1717 configuration, the COU encompasses a range of surgical construct configurations that may differ in offset geometry. Only one test condition was evaluated, limiting achievement to level 2. This is a documented shortfall acknowledged in the credibility assessment."
